Don't let me kick it down!

100
00:04:12,770 --> 00:04:13,650
One!

101
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,680
Two!

102
00:04:14,770 --> 00:04:15,610
Three!

103
00:04:17,130 --> 00:04:18,570
Hello, Mr. Zhang!

104
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,520
