118
00:05:05,450 --> 00:05:07,280
I was just watching them.

119
00:05:07,690 --> 00:05:09,330
Little imp, were you gambling?

120
00:05:09,330 --> 00:05:10,170
Cricket betting?

121
00:05:11,090 --> 00:05:11,930
No!

122
00:05:12,010 --> 00:05:12,850
Seriously.

123
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:14,960
