128
00:05:31,890 --> 00:05:32,730
Move aside!

129
00:05:35,450 --> 00:05:36,920
Studying?

130
00:05:39,650 --> 00:05:40,960
Watching and learning.

131
00:05:41,450 --> 00:05:42,570
At the same time?

132
00:05:42,970 --> 00:05:44,160
