to take a hand-copied book!

166
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,720
Look! Look!

167
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,720
Yeah, it's you.

168
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,690
Come on!

169
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:30,040
