179
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,570
Come on! No way!

180
00:07:43,570 --> 00:07:44,600
Don't you remember?

181
00:07:44,890 --> 00:07:46,650
Back then, you took Liu Dagui
and the others

182
00:07:46,650 --> 00:07:47,520
