191
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,450
Get me some chili sauce.

192
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:16,890
My analysis is this.

193
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,250
Since the punishment

194
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:20,010
