200
00:08:44,170 --> 00:08:45,170
Hey, Brother Xiao.

201
00:08:45,410 --> 00:08:46,330
What's up?

202
00:08:46,330 --> 00:08:47,840
Aren't we the best of buddies?

203
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,210
Tell me what's going on.

204
00:08:50,210 --> 00:08:51,170
Just tell me, yes or no.

205
00:08:53,110 --> 00:08:54,090
Yes, yes.

206
00:08:55,370 --> 00:08:56,210
This

207
00:08:56,210 --> 00:08:57,050
