214
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,930
Don't ask.

215
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,640
- Just hide it.
- Wait, wait!

216
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:09,050
Unless you explain clearly.

217
00:09:11,090 --> 00:09:12,000
Just for a few days!

218
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,320
