261
00:12:44,930 --> 00:12:45,930
Jizhong.

262
00:12:52,290 --> 00:12:53,640
Xuanshu.

263
00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:56,890
Mingmen.

264
00:12:58,330 --> 00:12:59,170
Alright,

265
00:12:59,290 --> 00:13:01,240
